‘How to Trust‘ with Nexa Music is Out Now! ✨

I’ve been waiting so long to share this with you all — and it still feels surreal. ✨

Incredibly grateful to be part of @nexamusicexperience , and deeply honoured that @arrahman sir believed in me and gave me the chance to be part of this vision.

Big love to @zero_fucking_chill for crafting the music that helped bring my vision to life.

Thank you @shreydidit for making this banging visual ❤️

And thank you all for bring a part of my journey, your support and encouragement is what keeps me going — can’t wait to share more music, and more of my heart with you. 🌌🎵

Some moments aren’t just milestones - they’re answers to silent prayers.

I had the rare honor of speaking with A.R. Rahman Sir — a legend, an inspiration, and the soundtrack of my childhood.

This moment means so much to me cause he was also my dad’s favorite artist.

From his caller tune to his bluetooth requests, Rahman Sir’s music was always playing in our lives.

Though my father isn’t here to witness this, I know he’s smiling from above.

This wasn’t just a dream — it was a manifestation rooted in belief.

“Believe you can, and you will.”

Hold your vision. Stay grateful. And have faith in God’s timing. 🙏🏽

Thank you @zero_fucking_chill for believing in me and constantly supporting me, I wouldn’t be here without you.

Thank you @nexamusicexperience for making this possible for us !
